Dinner
STARTER
Heirloom tomato salad with creamy burrata cheese
(fresh milk mozzarella), olive oil fried croutons, wild
rocket and aged balsamic
MAIN COURSE
Lamb osso buco on saffron risotto milanese, fried olives
stuffed with spicy lamb sausage and salsa verde
New Zealand hapuka with sunchoke puree, black truffle
crepes, sauteed pea tenderils and slow roasted tomatoes
Wood roasted chicken breast with green garlic mashed
potato, cavolo nero (braised Tuscan greens), mushroom
bolognaise, Madeira and chicken jus
DESSERT
Carrot cake cream cheese mousse with carrot leather
and citrus creme fraiche
CHEESE
A selection of fine New Zealand cheese
Beverages
A premium selection of fine New Zealand wines is
available on your flight today. This selection, chosen by
our panel of recognised wine consultants, will be detailed
by your flight attendants. New Zealand's award winning
42 Below vodka is also available in cocktails created
for Air New Zealand.
A full selection of beer, spirits, soft drinks and hot beverages
is available throughout the flight.
Snacks
Help yourself from our range of snacks available for you
to enjoy during your flight.
Breakfast
FRUIT, CEREAL AND BAKERY
Fruit selection with assorted cereals and yoghurt
Croissants with fruit conserve
HOT BREAKFAST
Creamy scrambled eggs with chives, chicken and sun dried
tomato sausages, grilled bacon and mushrooms
Orange brioche French toast with passionfruit cream
and manuka honey and apple syrup
Please accept our apologies should your first choice not be available
due to previous customer selection
